
---

# 🚫 `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# =========================
# OS / system files
# =========================
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# =========================
# Editor / IDE
# =========================
.vscode/
.idea/
*.sublime-workspace
*.sublime-project

# =========================
# Logs
# =========================
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# =========================
# Dependencies (if you ever add Node tooling)
# =========================
node_modules/

# =========================
# Build / output folders (future-proofing)
# =========================
dist/
build/
out/

# =========================
# Temporary files
# =========================
*.tmp
*.temp